"text-lg text-slate-400">Communicative Density (D):</p><p id="mamc-density-score" class="text-5xl font-bold text-white">1.00</p></div></div><div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-xl"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center text-white">Comparative Analysis</h2><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-6"><input type="text" id="mamc-profile-name" placeholder="Enter profile name..." class="flex-grow p-2 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white"><button id="mamc-save-profile-btn" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700">Save Profile</button></div><div class="w-full h-80"><canvas id="mamc-comparison-chart"></canvas></div></div></div></div></div>`;
